ou will agree to my using a penname.

For reasons of my own, I do not wish to publish it under my name, for the time being, at least. Will you agree to respect my incognito?1





Sincerely,

Vladimir Nabokov





TO: PASCAL COVICI

CC, 1 p.

Ithaca, N.Y.





January 23, 1955

